@startuml
[*] --> Start
State "Start" as start
start --> AddGoods: [Add new goods to inventory]
state "Add Goods" as add_goods
add_goods --> UpdatePrice: [Update price of existing items in inventory]
state "Update Price" as update_price
update_price --> RemoveGoods: [Remove goods from inventory that are no longer required]
state "Remove Goods" as remove_goods
remove_goods --> IdentifyExpiredGoods: [Identify expired goods and notify user about removal]
state "Identify Expired Goods" as identify_expired_goods
identify_expired_goods --> PlaceOrder: [Place order to supplier for additional goods when required]
state "Place Order" as place_order
place_order --> GenerateInvoice: [Generate invoice for order once it is placed]
state "Generate Invoice" as generate_invoice
generate_invoice --> SearchItems: [Search for items available in inventory and select them for purchase]
state "Search Items" as search_items
search_items --> CalculateDiscountTax: [Calculate applicable discount and tax based on selected items]
state "Calculate Discount Tax" as calculate_discount_tax
calculate_discount_tax --> GenerateReceipt: [Generate receipt for customer after purchase]
state "Generate Receipt" as generate_receipt
generate_receipt --> ReplaceItemCancelReceipt: [Replace item or cancel receipt during billing process if needed]
state "Replace Item Cancel Receipt" as replace_item_cancel_receipt
replace_item_cancel_receipt --> RecordCustomerRequests: [Record customer requests for items that may not be currently available]
state "Record Customer Requests" as record_customer_requests
record_customer_requests --> ViewSummaryReport: [View summary report of all transactions carried out in system at any point]
state "View Summary Report" as view_summary_report

start -->* AddGoods: [Add new goods to inventory]
add_goods -->* UpdatePrice: [Update price of existing items in inventory]
update_price -->* RemoveGoods: [Remove goods from inventory that are no longer required]
remove_goods -->* IdentifyExpiredGoods: [Identify expired goods and notify user about removal]
identify_expired_goods -->* PlaceOrder: [Place order to supplier for additional goods when required]
place_order -->* GenerateInvoice: [Generate invoice for order once it is placed]
generate_invoice -->* SearchItems: [Search for items available in inventory and select them for purchase]
search_items -->* CalculateDiscountTax: [Calculate applicable discount and tax based on selected items]
calculate_discount_tax -->* GenerateReceipt: [Generate receipt for customer after purchase]
generate_receipt -->* ReplaceItemCancelReceipt: [Replace item or cancel receipt during billing process if needed]
replace_item_cancel_receipt -->* RecordCustomerRequests: [Record customer requests for items that may not be currently available]
record_customer_requests -->* ViewSummaryReport: [View summary report of all transactions carried out in system at any point]

view_summary_report --> [*]
@enduml
